THE LOOP · LUP — the feedback closure: the swarm consenses, the shadow names itself, the name becomes new bright matter, repeat. Node-verified honest result: SELF-LIMITING — it fills its own field until consensus becomes impossible (~round 13) and halts itself. A lens on self-referential pipelines: the field has to stay bigger than the loop…
